Problem link : https://leetcode.com/problems/score-of-a-string/description/?envType=daily-question&envId=2024-06-01


Java Solution:
class Solution {
    public int scoreOfString(String s) {
        int n = s.length();
        int ans = 0;
        for(int i=0;i<n-1;i++){
            int dif = Math.abs(s.charAt(i)-s.charAt(i+1));
            ans+=dif;
        }
        return ans;
    }
}

C++ Solution:
class Solution {
public:
    int scoreOfString(string s) {
        int n = s.length();
        int ans = 0;
        for(int i=0;i<n-1;i++){
            int dif = abs(s[i]-s[i+1]);
            ans+=dif;
        }
        return ans;
    }
};
